;;
;; The key is to prove that 
;; 
;; (state-set-local-at ....  (invalidate-category2-value ....))
;;
;; produce the same effect of 
;;
;; (bcv::modifylocalvariable ....)
;;
;; unfortunately, these two functions are quite different!!! 
;;
